{"tid":2107914,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英國將派遣航母戰鬥群部署遠東","createTime":"2020-07-14T07:47:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-14T13:22:55.000Z","uid":227801,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"ed09c5c465f6320ed23318121eb362ffd4d56711","tid":2107914,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T07:47:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200714/GSE5BPYZCAQAAXEGCWSYGDEXCU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200714%2FGSE5BPYZCAQAAXEGCWSYGDEXCU%2F&d=nqzd6QM3TLyrPp4uhCfCn2Hyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=9d9ae77e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200714%2FGSE5BPYZCAQAAXEGCWSYGDEXCU%2F&h=93435493\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200714/GSE5BPYZCAQAAXEGCWSYGDEXCU/</a><br />\n國際政治波橘雲詭，逐漸出現「天下圍中」之局勢。據英國《泰晤士報》（The Times）今日引述國防消息指，英國軍方正計劃將新航母「伊利沙伯女王號」（HMS Queen Elizabeth R08）部署在遠東地區，以抗衡中國日益增加的威脅。待明年初，伊利沙伯女王號所組成的戰鬥群，將展開首航，到訪遠東與美、日等盟友展開軍演。<br />\n<br />\n報道謂，造價達31億英鎊（約301億港元）的伊利沙伯女王號或於今年秋天完成訓練，比姊妹艦「威爾斯親王號」（HMS Prince of Wales R09）早18個月，並將於明年組成戰鬥群，展開首次遠航，預料會前往遠東地區與盟友進行軍演，其間亦會作為「浮動交易會場」，提供與盟友討論協議的平台。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，由伊利沙伯女王號所組成的戰鬥群，將會配備兩個中隊的F-35B隱形戰機，部份戰機或會由美國海軍提供，戰鬥群中還會有兩艘45型導彈驅逐艦及兩艘23型護衞艦。英國軍方還計劃待威爾斯號完成訓練後，不除排亦將派往遠東地區。<br />\n<br />\n不過，英國軍方的方案是，其中一艘新航母將部署在北大西洋支援北約，另一艘部署在印太地區，形成一個以英軍為首的盟軍部隊，對抗中國日益上升的威脅。<br />\n伊利沙伯女王號艦長基德（Jerry Kyd）表示，皇家海軍將重回印太地區，或會以航母戰鬥群的形式，持續在區內出現；又指英軍的F35隱形戰機亦將透過美日的基地部署在區內。<br />\n<br />\n英國國防部發言人則指，暫時仍未決定伊利沙伯女王號的未來部署。<br />\n<br />\n《泰晤士報》/ 《每日快報》"},{"pid":"fb31770e7de3db4be7cb11abe152ff3b5732a96c","tid":2107914,"uid":227801,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T07:49:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Y0NhSRaoAgaVTo0T_dZmpjxaKqM=/640x360/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/4HLSZO3ZN4REDBGVDVV7BNHYPM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FY0NhSRaoAgaVTo0T_dZmpjxaKqM%3D%2F640x360%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F4HLSZO3ZN4REDBGVDVV7BNHYPM.jpg&h=263c6121&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9dc750637798c8561cab718843b2c3d1536cd3e9","tid":2107914,"uid":49044,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T07:50:35.000Z","msg":"係咪用緊柴油果隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0719216223151709c3be6ccdc8087feb4dd0715a","tid":2107914,"uid":58209,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T07:51:51.000Z","msg":"美帝一早派左3隻去南海啦<br />\n你日落國依家先出？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab45c28c03eb54e0a938031376d55f3120156884","tid":2107914,"uid":256783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T07:52:08.000Z","msg":"排水量 70,600公噸（69,500長噸；77,800短噸）[1][2][3]<br />\n全長 280米<br />\n全寬 70米<br />\n吃水 11米<br />\n燃料 柴油<br />\n動力 勞斯萊斯MT30燃氣輪機"},{"pid":"15d670d02017a84d8451c3fb99c64f07f5ed3b15","tid":2107914,"uid":256783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T07:53:12.000Z","msg":"最高速度 25節以上<br />\n續航距離 10,000海里<br />\n乘員 1,450艦員<br />\n射控裝置 2 x Type 909 GWS-30 火控雷達<br />\n偵搜系統 SMART-L雷達<br />\nType 1022/965P 對空雷達<br />\nType 996/992Q 3-D雷達<br />\nType 2050 / 2016搜索聲納<br />\nType 162 海底描繪聲納<br />\n武器裝備 2 x 20mm 方陣快砲<br />\n2 x 對空砲20mm L/70 KBA 於GAM-B01單座砲塔<br />\n艦載機 50架（包括40架F35戰鬥機） 極限可擴充至70架<br />\n其它 Type 1007 導航雷達"},{"pid":"705acf4362aec87cb056d4b34db775d02cda67ec","tid":2107914,"uid":49044,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"0719216223151709c3be6ccdc8087feb4dd0715a","tid":2107914,"uid":58209,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T07:51:51.000Z","msg":"美帝一早派左3隻去南海啦<br />\n你日落國依家先出？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T07:53:53.000Z","msg":"美帝有11 隻，出左3隻<br />\n大米國得惟一